					 <strong>-53 kg. Purchasing products for my PP menu for a week</strong><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>I'll show you out</span><span></span><a><u><b>The slimness regatta </b></u></a><span>. Since Monday, I have made my ideal menu for the week, using a </span><span></span><a><u><b>glycemic load </b></u></a><span>and KBZHU. Was very a lot of calculations, I managed to balance all the indicators with great difficulty.</span></p><div><div><div></div></div></div><div><div></div></div><h3><span>What did I buy for this PP-ration?</span></h3><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Celery stalk. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>For stewing meat in a slow cooker, I need vegetables. The best option is zucchini, celery, onions, and carrots. Celery stalks I bought already peeled-a package of 250 gr 83 RUB. Zucchini 590 gr 86 RUB </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Squashes. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>For lunch, I have a salad of fresh cucumbers and green peas planned. Cucumbers took short-fruited 500 gr for 92 RUB. Peas I have there is-frozen in the refrigerator - I will use it.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Cucumbers. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Corn is needed as a side dish for dinner with meat stewed with vegetables. In the Bank was not, bought boiled in a package of 2 PCs for 116 rubles. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Corn. Photo author's.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>I use a pear for a second Breakfast with cottage cheese. I bought Packham pears 1.4 kg for 162 rubles. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Pears. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Oatmeal is my main Breakfast. I've been buying large whole grains lately. I soak them overnight in water to keep them fresh. the flakes are swollen and I cook them in the morning like a normal porridge with the addition of a small amount of milk. In a package of 400 g, the price is 35 rubles. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Rolled oats. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Cottage cheese is needed for a second Breakfast. From it, I make either a casserole or eat it as it is with natural yogurt without additives and pears. In the dish, I add a little sugar substitute-erythritol. This time I bought cottage cheese from melted milk 5%, the cost of packaging 200 gr 95 RUB (in "Magnet" there is a similar curd at 35 RUB/pack - how do you like it, have you tried it?). </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Cottage cheese 5%. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Milk in the bottle of 3.2% 900 ml - 56. Ryazhenka 3.2% - 38 rubles. Natural yogurt 1.5 % - 69 RUB. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Molochkos. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>I have beef planned on the menu for dinner - it is this that I will stew with vegetables. I bought a shoulder blade without a bone of category a-496 gr for 320 rub.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Beef. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Pollock goes for lunch. I bake it in the oven with onions in yogurt. I took a package of fillets without skin 734 gr for 302 RUB. </span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Fillet of Pollock. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Chicken when losing weight - universal means. In its baked form, it can be used in salads, in rolls, on sandwiches. I have it planned for an afternoon snack with cucumber salad. A broiler chicken carcass pulled 1.5 kg, the price is 289 rubles.</span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Chicken. Photo author's.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Egg whites. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span>Egg white is very convenient in the preparation of omelets for Breakfast. In a package of 500 g 15 PCs of egg whites. Price 120 rubles.</span></p><p><span><i>It was not without spontaneous purchases - my husband took to himself potato chips with a discount of 66 rubles., the child took cookies "Machine mushrooms" for 65 rubles.</i></span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Potato chips. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><h3><span>The total amount for the receipt is 2,447 rubles.</span></h3><p><span><i>I'll still have to stop by the store a couple of times this week for more.</i></span></p><blockquote><span><i>Yes! And I almost forgot! I'll be eating chocolate this week! Yes, Yes, this black one with nuts on it. I bought a tile "Inspiration" bitter with almonds 75% cocoa. Why do I do this? I recently read this advice from a nutritionist. After eating - eat chocolate candy. Here, I decided to check this version. This week, I made my menu not only taking into account KBZHU, but also carefully calculating glycemic load. </i></span></blockquote><p><span><i>My husband still went to the "traffic Light". There he bought a package of cheap fresh-frozen unpeeled Pollock at 127 rubles/kg. In a package of 2.4 kg for 307 rubles. And a pack of frozen strawberries for 138 rubles (cheaper than in "Magnet", "Pyaterochka", "Globus"). The package contains 1 kg. I grind the strawberries in a blender, then I add sweetener and get a good sweet and low-calorie sauce for cheesecakes, cottage cheese or PP desserts.  </i></span></p><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Frozen Pollock. Photo of the author.</span></figcaption></figure><figure><div><div></div><div><img></div><div></div></div><meta><figcaption><span>Strawberry. Production - Egypt. Photo author's.</span></figcaption></figure><p><span><u><b>See also: </b></u></span></p><p><span><i>Purchasing food for the festive table:</i></span></p><div><div><div></div></div></div><p><span><i>My birthday is barbecue style:</i></span></p><div><div><div></div></div></div><p><span><i>Thank you for your likes and subscriptions! All beauty and slimness.</i></span><span> üåàüåºüëç<br></span><span><i><b>Subscribe to me in:</b></i></span><span></span></p><ul><li><span><u><i>Zen -</i></u></span><span> </span><span></span><a><u><i></i></u></a></li><li><span><u><i>YouTube - </i></u></span><span></span><span></span><a><u><i>- HPA</i></u></a></li><li><span><u><i>Twitter -</i></u></span><span> </span><span></span><a><u><i></i></u></a></li><li><span><u><i>Pinterest -</i></u></span><span> </span><span></span><a><u><i></i></u></a></li><li><span><u><i>Odnoklassniki -</i></u></span><span> </span><span></span><a><u><i></i></u></a></li></ul><p><span></span></p><div></div>
					
